FreeSpeak is a simple frontend to already existing online translators.

The installation is described in the INSTALL file.

SYSTEM REQUIRMENTS
Python 2.4 or higher
GTK+ 2.12 or higher
PyGTK 2.12 or higher
PyGObject 2.12 or higher
GnomePython 2.10 or higher
Dbus-Python
Python LXML

KEYBOARD SHORTCUTS
Ctrl+T	New text translation
Ctrl+W	New web translation
Ctrl+P	Shows preferences dialog
Ctrl+A	Shows about dialog
Ctrl+Q	Quit 
Ctrl+T	Translate
